Azure DevOps Services 
Yeh section mein 5 core services ka overview deta hai jo Azure DevOps provide karta hai:


1. Azure Boards
Agile project management tool.
Work items (User Stories, Tasks, Bugs) create karke manage karte hain.
Kanban boards, backlogs, sprints planning sab yahan hota hai.
Scrum, Agile, CMMI, Basic — koi bhi process template use kar sakte ho.

2. Azure Repos
Source control — code store karne ka jagah.
Git repositories host karta hai (private, unlimited).
Pull requests, branch policies, code review — sab yahan.
GitHub ke saath bhi integrate hota hai.

3. Azure Pipelines
CI/CD ka engine — sabse powerful part.
Code push hone pe automatic build, test, aur deploy.
YAML pipelines aur Classic Editor (GUI) dono support karta hai.
Any language, any platform — .NET, Java, Node, Python, Go, etc.
Cloud (Azure, AWS, GCP) kahi bhi deploy kar sakte ho.

4. Azure Test Plans
Manual testing aur exploratory testing ke liye.
Test plans, test suites, aur test cases manage karte hain.
Browser extension se directly screenshots/notes leke bugs raise kar sakte hain.

5. Azure Artifacts
Package management — apni libraries, NuGet, npm, Maven, Python packages host karne ke liye.
Team ke andar reusable code packages share karne ka tarika.
Upstream sources se public packages (like npm registry) bhi cache kar sakte hain.
